 * The insight explained in 3-4 sentences.
 */
---

<section class="thesis section-dark section" aria-labelledby="thesis-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="label reveal">The Philosophy</p>
    <h2 id="thesis-heading" class="thesis-heading reveal">
      Let's evolve, with no human left behind.
    </h2>
    <div class="thesis-body reveal">
      <p>
        "No Human Left Behind" is a commitment, and a tension I live with daily.
      </p>
      <p>
        I love AI. I'm a power user. It's transformed how I work, what I can
        build, how I think, and how I create. It hasn't just made me faster.
        It's enhanced my creativity and entire process. I want others to
        experience that.
      </p>
      <p>
        And I'm deeply aware of the damage it can cause. To jobs, to
        creativity, to human connection. I've struggled with this. It's
        not resolved.
      </p>
      <p>
        That tension is the engine. Something harder than doomerism or
        hype: using the thing I'm worried about,
        responsibly, while helping others do the same.
      </p>
      <p>
        As an AI Enablement Engineer at Vanguard, I coach teams
        on AI adoption, mentor junior engineers, and drive culture with
        a responsible AI lens. The philosophy isn't just a belief. It's
        operationalized. It's literally the job.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a href="/about" class="thesis-link link-light">
      The human behind the mission
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .thesis-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .thesis-body {
    max-width: var(--max-width-prose);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .thesis-body p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-gray-light);
  }

  .thesis-body p + p {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .thesis-link {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
